data.description: Meticulous Inside and Out. 3 Bedrooms with 1st floor office or guest room. Open Floor Plan with gourmet kitchen featuring SS appliances and Oversized Center Island. Radiant Heat Flooring through out First floor and Upstairs Bathrooms. Brazilian Cherry Hardwood Flooring and Ceramic Tile. Primary Bedroom is 20x17 with Walk-In Closet and Renovated Bathroom w double sinks. Lutron Lighting with Electronic Blinds. Whole House Attic Fan, Solar Panels and Sprinkler System. Walk Out to Large Deck with Purgola and Built in Hot Tub (newer 2016). Landscaped/Fenced in Yard . Storage Shed has electric and water. Outside Shower Stall for after the beach or Hot tub. Basement and Walk up attic provide plenty of storage. NO FLOOD INSURANCE required. Must See Inside/Out this home....
